title: Back from NYC, Michael Greene runs for Syracuse Common Council in 4th District
text: SYRACUSE, N.Y. - While he was living in Manhattan and working for New York City's economic development agency, Michael Greene was thinking about Syracuse. One of the last papers he wrote for his MBA degree was on economic development strategies...
